  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">moderate</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Spewing Vents</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to trigger node growth and begin the <VAL_ON>grafting process<>.<br><br>Each node is genetically unique, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Potential improvements include: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">damage</span>, <span class=\"name name-stellar\">fire rate</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">overheat times</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">喷口</span>的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">普通</span>提升。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>触发节点增长并开始<VAL_ON>嫁接过程<>。<br><br>每个节点在基因上都是独一无二的，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">伤害</span>，<span class=\"name name-stellar\">射速</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">过热前使用次数</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">噴射口</span>的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">一般</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 觸發節點生長，並開始<VAL_ON>移植程序<>。<br><br>每個節點的基因皆不相同，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能強化的項目包括：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">傷害值</span>、<span class=\"name name-stellar\">射擊速度</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">過熱次數</span>。"
  },
